This UK Type G smart plug is supplied preflashed and preconfigured with Tasmota or ESPHome. It uses an ESP32-C3 with 4 MB flash and BL0937 power monitoring.

Case is glued shut and there is no direct serial port access. Flashing and firmware changes are done over Wi-Fi.
